["sum","In summary, volunteering has clear benefits; <em>however</em>, the method of implementation determines whether it truly achieves its goals.","adv. 连接副词表转折",M+" volunteering has clear benefits; "+M+" however, the method of implementation determines + "+OBJ+" whether it truly achieves its goals","总之，志愿服务有明显的好处；然而，实施方式决定了它是否真正实现其目标。"]
