["sum","In conclusion, true <em>discipline</em> is not imposed from the outside but cultivated from within — and the best educational systems nurture both.","n. 单数，作主语",M+" true discipline is not imposed from the outside but cultivated from within — "+M+" and the best educational systems nurture both","总之，真正的纪律不是从外部强加的，而是从内心培养的——最好的教育系统兼顾两者。"]
