["prof","Some educators have noticed a <em>tendency</em> for students to view volunteering as merely resume-building.","n. 单数，作 noticed 的宾语",M+" Some educators have noticed a tendency + 介词短语(for students to view volunteering as merely resume-building)","一些教育者注意到学生倾向于将志愿服务仅视为简历的加分项。"],
["stu","I've noticed a <em>tendency</em> among my peers to dismiss history as boring and irrelevant.","n. 单数，作宾语",M+" I've noticed a tendency + 介词短语(among my peers) + 不定式(to dismiss history as boring and irrelevant)","我注意到我的同龄人有一种将历史视为无聊和无关紧要的倾向。"],
["stu","There is a <em>tendency</em> in education to focus on standardized testing at the expense of creative thinking.","n. 单数，在 there be 句型中",M+" There is a tendency + 介词短语(in education) + 不定式(to focus on standardized testing) + 介词短语(at the expense of creative thinking)","教育中存在一种以牺牲创造性思维为代价来关注标准化考试的趋势。"],
["write","The <em>tendency</em> to equate mandatory service with genuine altruism is, in my view, fundamentally misguided.","n. 单数，作主语",M+" The tendency + 不定式(to equate mandatory service with genuine altruism) + is, 插入语(in my view), fundamentally misguided","在我看来，将强制服务等同于真正利他主义的倾向从根本上是错误的。"],
["write","I believe there is a dangerous <em>tendency</em> to overlook the emotional needs of boarding school students in favor of academic achievement.","n. 单数，在 there be 句型中",M+" I believe + "+OBJ+" there is a dangerous tendency + 不定式(to overlook the emotional needs of boarding school students) + 介词短语(in favor of academic achievement)","我认为存在一种危险的倾向，即为了学业成绩而忽视寄宿学校学生的情感需求。"],
["write","Andrew correctly identifies the <em>tendency</em> of institutions to prioritize compliance over genuine engagement.","n. 单数，作 identifies 的宾语",M+" Andrew correctly identifies the tendency + 介词短语(of institutions) + 不定式(to prioritize compliance over genuine engagement)","Andrew正确地指出了机构倾向于优先考虑顺从而非真正参与的趋势。"],
["arg","History reveals a recurring <em>tendency</em> for societies to repeat the mistakes of previous generations when they neglect the past.","n. 单数，作宾语",M+" History reveals a recurring tendency + 介词短语(for societies to repeat the mistakes of previous generations) + "+TIM+" when they neglect the past","历史揭示了社会在忽视过去时重复前几代人错误的反复趋势。"],
["arg","The <em>tendency</em> toward short-term thinking in education policy undermines efforts to build lasting civic values.","n. 单数，作主语",M+" The tendency + 介词短语(toward short-term thinking in education policy) + undermines efforts + 不定式(to build lasting civic values)","教育政策中短期思维的倾向破坏了建立持久公民价值观的努力。"],
["sum","Ultimately, we must resist the <em>tendency</em> to view education as merely job preparation and instead recognize its broader role in shaping responsible citizens.","n. 单数，作 resist 的宾语",M+" we must resist the tendency + 不定式(to view education as merely job preparation) + 并列(and instead) + recognize its broader role + 介词短语(in shaping responsible citizens)","最终，我们必须抵制将教育仅视为就业准备的倾向，转而认识到它在塑造负责任公民方面更广泛的作用。"]
